720481f-a.title: Manhattan: Hudson Street - North Moore Street
720481f-a.text:
Hudson Street, north from(No. 129) but not including North Moore Street,
showing the New York Central Railroad tracks and freight cars. The
prominent building shown is the Green Industrial Building,at the S.W.
corner of Hubert Street.
July 26, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
